\c 8
\nb
\v 1 Amadoda akoEfrayimi\x + 12.1. 2 Sam. 19.41. Isa. 9.21.\x* asesithi kuye: Iyini linto oyenze kithi ukuthi awusibizanga nxa usiyakulwa lamaMidiyani? Amsola ngamandla.
\v 2 Wasesithi kiwo: Ngenzeni khathesi \add uba\add* kulinganiswa lokwenu? Ukukhothozwa kwezithelo zevini koEfrayimi kakukuhle yini kulesivuno sevini sakoAbiyezeri\x + Isa. 24.13. Jer. 49.9. Obad. 1.5. Mika 7.1.\x*?
\v 3 UNkulunkulu unikele esandleni senu iziphathamandla zeMidiyani\x + 7.24,25; 3.28.\x*, uOrebi loZebi; ngangingenzani njengani? Kwasekudeda kuye ukuthukuthela kwabo\x + Zaga 15.1.\x* lapho ekhuluma lelilizwi.
\s UGidiyoni uthumba amakhosi eMidiyani
\p
\v 4 Lapho uGidiyoni efika eJordani wachapha, yena lamadoda angamakhulu amathathu\x + 7.6.\x* ayelaye, bediniwe kodwa bexotsha.
\v 5 Wasesithi emadodeni eSukothi\x + Gen. 33.17. Josh. 13.27.\x*: Ake liphe abantu abangilandelayo\x + Eks. 11.8.\x* amaqebelengwana ezinkwa, ngoba badiniwe, ngixotshana loZeba loZalimuna amakhosi eMidiyani.
\v 6 Lenduna zeSukothi zathi: Intende yesandla sikaZeba loZalimuna isisesandleni sakho yini\x + 1 Sam. 25.11. 1 Kho. 20.11.\x*, ukuthi siphe ibutho lakho isinkwa?
\v 7 UGidiyoni wasesithi: Ngakho nxa iN\nd kosi\nd* isinikele uZeba loZalimuna esandleni sami, ngizabhula inyama yenu ngameva enkangala langokhula oluhlabayo\x + 8.16.\x*.
\p
\v 8 Wasesenyuka lapho waya ePenuweli\x + Gen. 32.31.\x*, wakhuluma labo ngokufananayo; lamadoda ePenuweli amphendula njengamadoda eSukothi e\add m\add*phendulile.
\v 9 Wasekhuluma futhi emadodeni ePenuweli esithi: Ekubuyeni kwami ngokuthula\x + 1 Kho. 22.27,28.\x* ngizadiliza lo umphotshongo\x + 8.17.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Njalo uZeba loZalimuna babeseKarikori lenkamba yabo ilabo, phose inkulungwane ezilitshumi lanhlanu, bonke ababesele ebuthweni\x + 7.12.\x* lonke labantwana bempumalanga\x + 6.3.\x*, ngoba ababewile babengamadoda azinkulungwane ezilikhulu lamatshumi amabili abahwatsha inkemba.
\v 11 UGidiyoni wasesenyuka ngendlela yabahlala emathenteni empumalanga kweNoba leJogibeha\x + Nani 32.35,42.\x*, wayitshaya inkamba, ngoba inkamba yayilibele\x + 18.27.\x*.
\v 12 UZeba loZalimuna basebebaleka, wasexotshana labo, wathumba amakhosi amabili eMidiyani\x + Hlab. 83.11.\x*, uZeba loZalimuna, wethusa inkamba yonke.
\p
\v 13 Lapho uGidiyoni indodana kaJowashi esebuya evela empini phambi kokuphuma kwelanga,
\v 14 wabamba ijaha emadodeni eSukothi, walibuza; laselimbhalela iziphathamandla zeSukothi labadala bayo, amadoda angamatshumi ayisikhombisa lesikhombisa.
\v 15 Wasefika emadodeni eSukothi, wathi: Khangelani oZeba loZalimuna elalingiklolodela ngabo lisithi: Intende yesandla sikaZeba loZalimuna isisesandleni sakho yini\x + 8.6,7.\x*, ukuthi siphe amadoda akho asediniwe isinkwa?
\v 16 Wasethatha abadala bomuzi\x + 8.6,7.\x*, lameva enkangala lokhula oluhlabayo, wenza amadoda eSukothi aqedisise ngawo.
\v 17 Lomphotshongo wePenuweli\x + 8.9. 1 Kho. 12.25.\x* wawudiliza, wabulala amadoda omuzi.
\p
\v 18 Wasesithi kuZeba lakuZalimuna: Ngamadoda anjani elawabulala eThabhori\x + Josh. 19.12. Hlu. 6.2.\x*? Basebesithi: Njengawe babenjalo, ngulowo njengesimo sendodana yenkosi.
\v 19 Wasesithi: Babengabafowethu, abantwana bakamama. Kuphila kukaJehova\x + Ruthe 3.13.\x*, uba belibayekele baphila, bengingayikulibulala.
\v 20 Wasesithi kuJetheri izibulo lakhe: Sukuma ubabulale. Kodwa umfana kayihwatshanga inkemba yakhe, ngoba wayesesaba ngoba esesengumfana.
\v 21 UZeba loZalimuna basebesithi: Sukuma wena uwele phezu kwethu, ngoba njengoba injalo indoda, \add anjalo\add* amandla ayo. Wasesukuma uGidiyoni wabulala uZeba loZalimuna\x + 1 Sam. 15.33; 22.17,18. 1 Kho. 2.34.\x*. Wasethatha izinyangana ezazisentanyeni zamakamela abo.
\s UGidiyoni wala ukubekwa inkosi
\p
\v 22 Amadoda akoIsrayeli asesithi kuGidiyoni: Sibuse, wena-ke, lendodana yakho, lendodana yendodana yakho, ngoba usisindisile esandleni samaMidiyani.
\v 23 Kodwa uGidiyoni wathi kibo: Mina kangiyikulibusa, lendodana yami kayiyikulibusa; iN\nd kosi\nd* izalibusa\x + 1 Sam. 12.12. 1 Sam. 8.7; 10.19; 12.17,19.\x*.
\p
\v 24 UGidiyoni wasesithi kibo: Ake ngicele isicelo kini; nginikani ngamunye icici lempango\x + Gen. 24.22.\x* yakhe. Ngoba babelamacici egolide, ngoba babengamaIshmayeli\x + Gen. 37.25; 39.1. Gen. 37.28,36.\x*.
\v 25 Basebesithi: Sizanika lokunika. Basebesendlala isembatho, baphosela lapho ngamunye icici lempango yakhe.
\v 26 Lesisindo samacici egolide ayewacelile sasingama\w shekeli\w** egolide ayinkulungwane lamakhulu ayisikhombisa, ngaphandle kwezinyangana\x + 8.21.\x*, leziceciso ezilengayo, lezembatho eziyibubende ezazisemakhosini eMidiyani\x + Esta 8.15. Zaga 31.22. Jer. 10.9. Hez. 27.7. Luka 16.19. Joha. 19.2,5. Isam. 17.4; 18.12,16.\x*, langaphandle kwamaketane ayesezintanyeni zamakamela awo\x + Zaga 1.9. Ngoma 4.9. Hlab. 73.6.\x*.
\v 27 UGidiyoni wasesenza \w i-efodi\w**\x + 17.5; 18.14,17. Eks. 28.6-35.\x* ngakho, wayibeka emzini wakhe, eOfira\x + 6.24.\x*. LoIsrayeli wonke waphinga lapho ngokuyilandela\x + 8.33. Hlab. 106.39. Eks. 34.15.\x*; yasisiba ngumjibila kuGidiyoni\x + Eks. 23.33.\x* lendlu yakhe.
\s Ukufa kukaGidiyoni
\p
\v 28 Ngokunjalo amaMidiyani ehliselwa phansi phambi kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli, kawaphindanga aphakamisa ikhanda lawo. Lelizwe laba lokuthula iminyaka engamatshumi amane\x + 3.11.\x* ensukwini zikaGidiyoni.
\p
\v 29 UJerubali indodana kaJowashi wayahlala-ke endlini yakhe.
\v 30 Njalo uGidiyoni wayelamadodana angamatshumi ayisikhombisa aphuma okhalweni lwakhe\x + 9.2,5.\x*, ngoba wayelabafazi abanengi.
\v 31 Lomfazi wakhe omncane owayeseShekema\x + 9.1. Josh. 17.7.\x* laye wamzalela indodana, wayitha ibizo \add lokuthi\add* nguAbhimeleki.
\p
\v 32 UGidiyoni indodana kaJowashi wasesifa eseluphele kuhle\x + Gen. 15.15; 25.8. Jobe 5.26.\x*, wangcwatshelwa engcwabeni likaJowashi uyise, eOfira yamaAbiyezeri\x + 6.24.\x*.
\v 33 Kwasekusithi lapho uGidiyoni esefile\x + 2.19.\x*, abantwana bakoIsrayeli baphenduka, baphinga ngokulandela oBhali\x + 8.27.\x*, bazimisela uBhali-Berithi\x + 9.4,46.\x* waba ngunkulunkulu.
\v 34 Njalo abantwana bakoIsrayeli kabayikhumbulanga iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wabo\x + Hlab. 78.42. Hlab. 106.13,21.\x* eyabophula esandleni sezitha zabo zonke inhlangothi zonke.
\v 35 Kabenzanga umusa endlini kaJerubali\x + 9.16-18. Josh. 2.12. Hlu. 1.24.\x*, \add ong\add*uGidiyoni, njengakho konke okuhle akwenza kuIsrayeli.